  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a there was a feeling of-- anti-- anti-Semitic feeling towards the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in my town, not violent.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember-- actually, I remember as little girl, they did like me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I congregated with the non-Jewish children, and I played with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember on one occasion, they was cross with me for some sort of reason.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they called me, 'Jewish girl, Jewish girl.' And that was a sort of insult [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] which I suppose to make me unhappy about.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Alright?] ?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And did it make you unhappy?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't like the comment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't make me unhappy, but I hate them for it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I was seven.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I myself-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I myself did not find so much-- I didn't [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] experience on-- on myself too much of the anti-Semitic things.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do remember the landlord was not Jewish with the house, and [LAUGHS] there wasn't such a comfort.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a lot of the places, the homes did not have their own bathrooms or toilets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a toilet which quite a few people did have to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the winter, it was very uncomfortable, because it was outside the-- And when something went wrong with the system, he always was very angry and cold.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] 'Well,' he said, 'Jews [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] are still used to-- not used to the comfort.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They should--' it's very hard to translate from Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He did think that the Jews should still use the toilet behind the house, [LAUGHS] you know, sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whenever something went wrong, he did use these terms, right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] otherwise, I don't think I did experience of too much anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
